{
  "stem": "24470.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a very difficult question to answer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I would say my personality, but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I often think if I wouldn't go through what I went through, would I be the same person?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always had interest in people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still have it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was always optimistic, and I still am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always loved reading, and I still read, and I learned from it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always loved learning, and I'm still learning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I think my experience made me-- perhaps, I'm not sure, because maybe I would be the same if I didn't go through experience-- maybe a deeper person and more compassionate, understanding, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And understanding that desperation and bad conditions are not the end, and it can change.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Also understanding that human spirit and the life within you and the mind, if it works, can really perform miracles and regain its strength and its life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because as I said before, in my childhood I had this relationship with God, but I didn't know much about Judaism.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the camp, I don't know if I thought about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after the camp, I returned to the same procedure, and I began to study Judaism, which I didn't know much.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I-- and I continuously study now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't belong to any particular-- I go to synagogue, of course-- but I don't belong to-- I don't call myself orthodox, conservative, or reformed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I call myself a learning Jewess.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there is so much to learn and so much that I didn't know about humanity, about relationships, about how to live.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there's so much beauty in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kept me alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe coincidence.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe a miracle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I didn't do anything to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I cannot really explain it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
